title: No. 23 Virginia Tech plays host to No. 3 NC State on Senior Day - VT hokiesports.com
content: No. 23 Virginia Tech plays host to No. 3 NC State on Senior Day  VT hokiesports.com
description: Blacksburg -- The Virginia Tech women's basketball team (21-7, 13-4) returns to the court on Sunday evening when they take on the No. 3 NC State Wolfpack (25-3, 16-1).
